> urban cyberpunk outerwear

// adaptive shell system

// post-urban conditions



We operate in an era of continuous disruption: political instability, algorithmic surveillance, artificial intelligence replacing human labor, accelerated urban rhythms.



Clothing is no longer seasonal, it is operational. Adaptive shell construction designed for prolonged use: regulates airflow and moisture under variable pressure, maintains structure during repetition, movement, temperature fluctuation. Not fashion as expression, fashion as response. cyberpunk cyberpunk aesthetic cyberpunk vibes cyberpunk style cyberpunk fashion blade runner deus ex mankind divided akira 1988 ghost in the shell techwear dystopian high fashion avant garde
